articles.author: Colby Applegate
articles.title: Roman Reigns Put On Trial, Jimmy Uso Taken Out On A Stretcher On 7/7 WWE SmackDown - Wrestlezone
articles.description: The Tribal Court of Roman Reigns kicked off the July 7 episode of WWE SmackDown and ended with Jimmy Uso getting stretchered out.
articles.content:
Tribal Court ended in chaos.
The July 7 episode of WWE SmackDown opened with The Usos conducting Tribal Court after Jey pinned Roman Reigns at Money in the Bank. Paul Heyman and Solo Sikoa initially… [+1111 chars]
